  var modeDescriptions={Map:'A high-level view of the project areas and their strongest connections.',Overview:'Project size, important areas, API surface, and architecture risks at a glance.',Modules:'Choose a module to see what uses it, what it depends on, and what lives inside it.',Routes:'Follow an HTTP request from its endpoint through application logic to data or external systems.',Async:'Follow messages and background jobs from publisher to topic or queue and then to their processor.',Services:'Explore business logic, injected dependencies, callers, and downstream resources.',Data:'See which parts of the application read, write, and own each data structure.',External:'Find integrations, libraries, and configuration used outside the application boundary.',Risks:'Review detected architecture concerns and open the code affected by each finding.',Code:'Browse files and functions with their architectural context.'};
